#

Bourbon Glazed Salmon

$25
450 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

Fish

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow CarbGluten-Free

Tags:

SeafoodAmerican CuisineDinner

Description

A succulent salmon fillet glazed with a sweet and tangy bourbon sauce, served with sautéed asparagus.

Ingredients

  • Salmon fillet: 4 oz
  • Bourbon: 1/4 cup
  • Brown sugar: 2 tbsp
  • Soy sauce: 2 tbsp
  • Garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • Asparagus: 1 bunch
  • Olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • Salt and pepper: to taste
